cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper deals with end-to-end control for robot manipulation and grasping, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves training a CNN to map observed images to velocities, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of domain randomisation to enable generalisation to real world images involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with accomplishing a multi-stage task, which involves system control (cs.SY).
